{"about_the_game":"We have always believed that God sent his son into the world to save us. But, what if that is not what happened? What if the world cannot be saved? <strong>The real story is about to be revealed</strong>. <br><br><strong>DESOLATIUM: PROLOGUE</strong> is a first-person point &amp; click Graphic Adventure based on Lovecraft Mythos. Live this horror story where you will have to visit mysterious locations, face lovecraftian creatures, find clues and combine objects to solve puzzles.<br><br>Get ready and dive into the beginning of the story, because the full game is coming soon:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE MYSTERIOUS LOCATIONS</h2><br>Explore a city outside the limits of time and space; meet mysterious characters who will guide you on your journey.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/GIF_EXPLORE.gif?t=1697616436\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FACE LOVECRAFTIAN CREATURES</h2><br>Face lovecraftian creatures that came from the most remote places in the universe to test your sanity.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/GIF_GHOUL.gif?t=1697616436\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FIND CLUES</h2><br>Find clues to move forward and uncover an intriguin backstory.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/GIF_LIBRO.gif?t=1697616436\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COMBINE OBJECTS TO SOLVE PUZZLES</h2><br>Interact with the objects around you to solve complex puzzles in order to get to the terrible presence of a cosmic entity of immense power: Cthulhu.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/GIF_COMBINE.gif?t=1697616436\" /><br><br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Innsmouth citizen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1640540/da4